import { Badge, HStack, Progress, VStack } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

const CustomBar = ({ high, low }) =>
    <VStack>
        <Progress
            value={50}
            colorScheme='teal'
            w={'full'}
        />
        <HStack justifyContent={'space-between'} w={'full'}></HStack>
        <Badge
            children={low}
            colorScheme='red'
        />
        <Text Font>24H Range</Text>
        <Badge
            children={high}
            colorScheme='green'
        />
    </VStack>



export default CustomBar
